Styling
Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling
Follow the existing color scheme using CSS variables (--background, --foreground, etc.)
Use the cn() utility from @/lib/utils for conditional class names
Reference the shadcn theme variables defined in tailwind.config.js

Always research existing styling before creating new components.

If you must import shadcn, use this command:

npx shadcn@latest add [import]
